                                <r3d:remarks>Availability of Arachne 3:
After a 20 year period of serving the archaeological community online, version 3 of Arachne can no longer be maintained as part of the open World Wide Web. 
Project partners who still require access to Arachne 3 are advised to contact the Research Archive for Ancient Sculpture at the Institute of Archaeology of the University of Cologne.
Note: Arachne 3 and 4 (iDAI.objects) manage the same database content (datasets and digitised images). They differ only in aspects of data presentation, and interactive functionality for querying and editing data.</r3d:remarks>
